{"tid":2184141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，頭先小巴屌完人，之後發現係鄰居嚟","createTime":"2020-09-01T11:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T07:19:33.000Z","uid":138834,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b04937882b7fd2ea0fe8b1071b5202ade689fa","tid":2184141,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"頭先有個呀叔A打尖，另一個呀叔B話佢<br />\n呀叔A仲駁嘴wo<br />\n咁我見呀叔B冇咩中氣，俾人恰返轉頭<br />\n咁冇理由一個人做正確嘅事反而要受氣架<br />\n<br />\n我就加入戰團屌柒打尖呀叔A<br />\n但可能大聲左少少，嚇到呀叔B都收埋聲<br />\n<br />\n之後落車時見到打尖呀叔A跟住我落<br />\n仲行埋同一條路<br />\n原本以為佢想偷襲我<br />\n我已經握住拳頭準備打交<br />\n<br />\n唉原來佢住我隔離再隔離<br />\n<br />\n以後出入要面左左了<br />\n<br />\n如果以後我屋企火燭，各位巴打記得幫我報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58b57344d2d27fa4286159256071b568a479984","tid":2184141,"uid":84102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"死仔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來係你 蝦我老人家"},{"pid":"3b4049d02c74e42a9cf9703f9445a7af161c4ff2","tid":2184141,"uid":275613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6cu83X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6cu83X.png&h=a48f768a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b87cf09684bc6fcb61e68e3d6e113a371b8d82e","tid":2184141,"uid":185565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"以後出入門口有幾督屎你知點解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f04dc3ff4ddcdd03915ca49373aa90ca1fa8646","tid":2184141,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b87cf09684bc6fcb61e68e3d6e113a371b8d82e","tid":2184141,"uid":185565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"以後出入門口有幾督屎你知點解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"人善人欺<img src=\"/assets/faces